entries.m1d: A bounty is hereby issued on a combatant who has become a serious threat to the Rebel alliance.
entries.m1s: The Rebel alliance sends its appreciation on a job well done.
entries.m2d: The Empire has hereby issued a bounty on an operative who has become a serious threat to law-abiding citizenry.
entries.m2s: The Empire appreciates your diligence and effort in successfully completing this bounty.
entries.m3d: A bounty has been posted by the Corporate Sector Authority for the death of a combatant.
entries.m1ds: A bounty is hereby issued on a smuggler who has been causing serious problems for the Rebel alliance.
entries.m2ds: The Empire has hereby issued a bounty on a smuggler who has been known to harbor and transport stolen Imperial goods.
entries.m3ds: A bounty has been posted by the Corporate Sector Authority for the death of a smuggler known to transport stolen property and/or illegal items.
